    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1917-04-10T20:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1917-04-10T20:00:00-05:00" n="320"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d320">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 763.72/3769</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Panama</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_PWJ1"
                        type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Price</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Panama</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1917-04-10T20:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">April 10, 1917, 8 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/> [<hi rend="italic">Received April 11, 3.30 a.m.</hi>]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Your April 9, 5 p.m. Proclamation of the President is so considered and I
                    construe it to be a declaration of war in its legal effect. <pb facs="0421"
                        n="249" xml:id="pg_249"/> Confirmation of said construction was obtained
                    this afternoon from Panaman President in the presence of Panaman Minister for
                    Foreign Affairs and Secretary of Government and Justice.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_PWJ1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Price</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
